      "updated": 1777472045639,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Each agent is responsible for doing\nactions on the machine it acces on behalf\nof the master. Actions like:\n- adding new worker node\n- kill exsiting worker node\n- send machine specs utilization\nThe agent doesn't store any data. ",
